---
title: Cheeky Chicken Chow Mein with Broccoli and Water Chestnuts
description: Chicken Chow Mein is a classic Chinese dish that has been adopted around the world, and Chow Mein simply means ‘fried noodles’. Our version contains crunchy water chestnuts and cabbage in a delicious sauce!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/cheeky-chicken-chow-mein-1d5ea14f.jpg
